Business Rules:
BR1: Each tour event must link a specific event to a tour.
BR2: A tour event must specify the sequence or order of the event in the tour.
BR3: A tour event must have a valid duration (start and end time).
System Requirements:
SYSREQ1: Establish a composite primary key in the TourEvent table combining tour_id and event_id.
SYSREQ2: Add a field to store the order of events in the tour, with a unique constraint on order per tour.
SYSREQ3: Implement a service-layer validation to ensure the start time and end time of the tour event are valid.